hn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Kinh nghim du lch H Ni Cc b ch, y " src="http://dulich9.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/kinh-nghiem-du-lich-ho-nui-coc-5.jpg" style="height:450px; width:600px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kinh nghim du lch H N&uacute;i Cc b &iacute;ch, y </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bn kh&ocirc;ng n&ecirc;n i H N&uacute;i Cc v&agrave;o m&ugrave;a &ocirc;ng, bi cnh sc kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; g&igrave; c sc, cng kh&ocirc;ng &ocirc;ng &uacute;c vui v, nht l&agrave; nhiu hot ng tham quan v&agrave; kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; kh&ocirc;ng c t chc do gii hn s lng kh&aacute;ch. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, nu bn ch n thun n vi H N&uacute;i Cc  ngh ngi, gii ta stress v&agrave; m m&igrave;nh trong kh&ocirc;ng gian ch&ugrave;a chin cng nh cnh sc thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n th&igrave; bn c&oacute; th i v&agrave;o m&ugrave;a n&agrave;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>i nh th n&agrave;o  n H N&uacute;i Cc? Hng dn c&aacute;ch di chuyn n H N&uacute;i Cc</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>H N&uacute;i Cc c&aacute;ch H&agrave; Ni khong 100km v&agrave; c&aacute;ch trung t&acirc;m TP.Th&aacute;i Nguy&ecirc;n khong 16km. Giao th&ocirc;ng t H&agrave; Ni, TP.H Ch&iacute; Minh v&agrave; c&aacute;c tnh kh&aacute;c trong c nc n H N&uacute;i Cc rt thun li. Trong b&agrave;i chia s&nbsp;<strong>kinh nghim du lch H N&uacute;i Cc t t&uacute;c i li, n chi</strong>&nbsp;n&agrave;y ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i s hng dn c&aacute;c bn c&aacute;ch di chuyn t H&agrave; Ni n H N&uacute;i Cc nh&eacute;:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&ndash; Xe &ocirc;-t&ocirc; kh&aacute;ch:</strong>&nbsp;C&aacute;c bn c&oacute; th &oacute;n xe M &igrave;nh-Th&aacute;i Nguy&ecirc;n ti bn xe&nbsp;M &igrave;nh, hoc bt k xe i Cao Bng, Bc Kn, L&agrave;o Cai, Y&ecirc;n B&aacute;i, Ph&uacute; Th&hellip;c&oacute; i qua bn xe Th&aacute;i Nguy&ecirc;n  i nh&eacute;. Khi l&ecirc;n xe bn nh bo ph xe cho xung  bn xe Th&aacute;i Nguy&ecirc;n nh&eacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi xung n bn xe, bn c&oacute; th thu&ecirc; xe &ocirc;m, taxi hoc i xe bus n H N&uacute;i Cc. a phn du kh&aacute;ch c&oacute;&nbsp;<strong>kinh nghim pht H N&uacute;i Cc t t&uacute;</strong>c bng xe kh&aacute;ch u chn xe bus l&agrave;m phng tin di chuyn t bn xe Th&aacute;i Nguy&ecirc;n l&ecirc;n H N&uacute;i Cc. Nu i bng xe bus th&igrave; bn ra cng bn r tr&aacute;i  bt bus H&agrave; Lan (03) hoc r tay phi, sang ng &oacute;n bus Mnh H&agrave; (02) n ng&atilde; ba H th&igrave; xung v&agrave; i bus o3 ti th&igrave; l&ecirc;n  i tip. Nh khi l&ecirc;n xe h&atilde;y bo l&aacute;i xe cho bn xung H N&uacute;i Cc l&agrave; c.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&ndash; Nu i bng xe m&aacute;y hoc &ocirc;-t&ocirc; t l&aacute;i:</strong>&nbsp;Bn i theo ng cao tc H&agrave; Ni-Th&aacute;i Nguy&ecirc;n c (qua s&acirc;n bay Ni B&agrave;i) l&ecirc;n TP.Th&aacute;i Nguy&ecirc;n. Sau &oacute; bn c&oacute; th i theo 1 trong 2 l tr&igrave;nh sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>TP. Th&aacute;i Nguy&ecirc;n &ndash; B u &ndash; C&ugrave; V&acirc;n &ndash; H&agrave; Thng &ndash; i T &ndash; H N&uacute;i Cc: Nu i theo l tr&igrave;nh tr&igrave;nh n&agrave;y bn s i qua l&agrave;ng ngh b&aacute;nh chng B u ni ting Nht Th&aacute;i Nguy&ecirc;n. Bn c&oacute; th dng li  mua b&aacute;nh chng, b&aacute;nh m&igrave;, mng t&hellip;Tuy nhi&ecirc;n l tr&igrave;nh n&agrave;y ng kh&aacute; xu v&agrave; kh&oacute; i. Do ang c&oacute; d &aacute;n khai th&aacute;c m  &acirc;y.</li>\r\n	<li>TP.Th&aacute;i Nguy&ecirc;n &ndash; &aacute;n &ndash; T&acirc;n Cng &ndash; H N&uacute;i Cc: Nu i theo l tr&igrave;nh n&agrave;y bn s c&oacute; c hi ngm nh&igrave;n nhng i ch&egrave; T&acirc;n Cng bt ng&agrave;n, tri rng 2 b&ecirc;n ng i. Nu may mn i v&agrave;o &uacute;ng m&ugrave;a ch&egrave; th&igrave; bn s b nhng i ch&egrave; thoai thoi, xanh rn  &acirc;y h&uacute;t hn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; C&aacute;c bn t c&aacute;c S&agrave;i G&ograve;n hoc c&aacute;c tnh min Nam mun du lch H N&uacute;i Cc c&oacute; th ra bn xe Min &ocirc;ng v&agrave; &oacute;n xe S&agrave;i G&ograve;n &ndash; Th&aacute;i Nguy&ecirc;n ri i theo hng dn d&agrave;nh cho xe kh&aacute;ch nh tr&ecirc;n. C&ograve;n c&aac